        <mxCell id="1" parent="0" />
        <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{&#xa;  &quot;data&quot;: &quot;@startuml AI Chatbot Support\ntitle Sequence Diagram - AI Chatbot Support\n\nactor Customer\nparticipant System\nparticipant OpenAI as \&quot;OpenAI API\\n(gpt-4o-mini)\&quot;\n\n== Open Chatbot ==\n\nCustomer -&gt; System : Click Chatbot Icon\\n(floating widget)\nSystem --&gt; Customer : Display Chat Window\n\n== Send Message ==\n\nCustomer -&gt; System : Type Question and Send\nSystem --&gt; Customer : Show Typing Indicator\n\nSystem -&gt; System : Build Messages Array\\n(system prompt + history\\n+ current message)\nSystem -&gt; OpenAI : POST chat/completions\\n(model: gpt-4o-mini,\\ntemperature: 0.3,\\nmax_tokens: 500)\nOpenAI --&gt; System : Return AI Response\n\nSystem --&gt; Customer : Display Bot Response\\nand Update Chat History\n\n== Conversation Continues ==\n\nCustomer -&gt; System : Ask Follow-up Question\nSystem -&gt; OpenAI : Send with Full History\\n(max 20 messages)\nOpenAI --&gt; System : Return Response\nSystem --&gt; Customer : Display Response\n\n== Clear Conversation ==\n\nCustomer -&gt; System : Click \&quot;Clear\&quot; Button\nSystem -&gt; System : Reset Chat History\nSystem --&gt; Customer : Clear Chat Window\n\n== Error Handling ==\n\nCustomer -&gt; System : Send Message\nSystem -&gt; OpenAI : API Call\nOpenAI --&gt; System : Connection Error\n\nSystem --&gt; Customer : Display Fallback Message\\n(\&quot;Sorry, try again later.\\nContact: +94 11 234 5678\&quot;)\n\n@enduml\n&quot;,&#xa;  &quot;format&quot;: &quot;svg&quot;&#xa;}" id="sx7TbSnaxO_tKYlK3s83-1">
